{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/adjust-the-padding-of-an-element","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-css","demoType":null,"title":"Podesi Unutrasnji Razmak Elementa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Hajde sada da na kratko ostavimo Cat Photo App i naucimo vise o stilizovanju HTML-a.</p>\n<p>Mozda ste vec primetili, ali svi HTML elementi su u osnovi mali pravougaonici.</p>\n<p>Tri vazna svojstva kontrolisu prostor oko svakog HTML elementa: <code>padding</code>, <code>border</code> i <code>margin</code>.</p>\n<p><code>padding</code> elementa kontrolise kolicinu prostora izmedju sadrzaja elementa i njegovog <code>border</code> okvira.</p>\n<p>Ovde vidimo da su plavi i crveni okvir smesteni unutar zutog okvira. Primetite da crveni okvir ima veci <code>padding</code> od plavog.</p>\n<p>Kada povecate <code>padding</code> plavog okvira, povecava se razmak izmedju teksta i ivice koja ga okruzuje.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad88fee1348bd9aedf08825","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Promenite <code>padding</code> svog plavog okvira tako da odgovara <code>padding</code> vrednosti crvenog okvira.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cED8ZC2","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301083,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/adjust-the-padding-of-an-element"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  .injected-text {\n    margin-bottom: -25px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .box {\n    border-style: solid;\n    border-color: black;\n    border-width: 5px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .yellow-box {\n    background-color: yellow;\n    padding: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .red-box {\n    background-color: crimson;\n    color: #fff;\n    padding: 20px;\n  }\n\n  .blue-box {\n    background-color: blue;\n    color: #fff;\n    padding: 10px;\n  }\n</style>\n<h5 class=\"injected-text\">margin</h5>\n\n<div class=\"box yellow-box\">\n  <h5 class=\"box red-box\">padding</h5>\n  <h5 class=\"box blue-box\">padding</h5>\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vasa <code>blue-box</code> klasa treba da postavi <code>padding</code> na <code>20px</code>.</p>","testString":"const blueBox = document.querySelector('.blue-box');\nconst paddingTop = window.getComputedStyle(blueBox)['padding-top'];\nassert.strictEqual(paddingTop, '20px');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#basic-css","dashedName":"adjust-the-padding-of-an-element","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-css","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/adjust-the-margin-of-an-element","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/use-an-id-attribute-to-style-an-element","id":"bad88fee1348bd9aedf08825","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>@media (max-width: 350px) {:root {--penguin-size: 200px; --penguin-skin: black;}}</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/adjust-the-padding-of-an-element"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}